sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as Database

    U->>FE: Click "Add Category"
    FE->>API: POST /api/categories {title}
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO todos (title, item_type)
    DB-->>API: {id, title, item_type: 'category'}
    API-->>FE: 201 Created
    FE-->>U: Display new category

    U->>FE: Add todo under category
    FE->>API: POST /api/todos {title, parentId}
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO todos (title, parent_id, item_type)
    DB-->>API: {id, title, parent_id, item_type: 'todo'}
    API-->>FE: 201 Created
    FE-->>U: Display todo under category
